dataIdInfo.idAbs: This point data layer represents street addresses for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Fond_du_Lac_Addresses_2015.gdb.[The fire address layer depicts fire address locations in Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin.Last published: May 21, 2015.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[This data was created to cartographically inform citizens as well as public and private officials of the location of fire addresses in Fond du Lac County.]
